docs.abstract: Demonstrations in Charlotte, NC, where violence has erupted in wake of fatal police shooting of black man Keith L Scott have given explosive new issue to presidential race in North Carolina; Hillary Clinton and Donald J Trump are trying to sway voters in crucial swing state.

docs.lead_paragraph: Emails from a Democratic operative posted online reveal not only detailed schedules of officials but also personal information of donors and Secret Service agents.
docs.abstract: Hackers post hundreds of emails from low-level Democratic operative Ian Mellul containing detailed schedules and movements of Vice Pres Joseph R Biden Jr, first lady Michelle Obama and Hillary Clinton during campaign fund-raisers and political events; emails include contacts for Secret Service agents and Social Security numbers of donors; documents posted reveal extent to which White House officials, Clinton campaign staff and Secret Service agents have exchanged sensitive information with people using personal email accounts.

headline.main: Email Hack Details Movements of Joe Biden, Michelle Obama and Hillary Clinton
